Skeletons in Ullek play a small role in the Dealing with Scabaras quest. They are located in the raised area near Lead archaeologist Abigail, along with dried zombies and mummies. Their location is affected by desert heat. These skeletons can be killed for Scabarite notes to complete the Scabarites Notes miniquest.
